info.description:
Complete API Collection untuk Platform Evaluasi Kebijakan Lingkungan Sekolah.

## Base URL
Semua request menggunakan base URL: `{{baseUrl}}/api/v1`

## Response Format

**Success (List):**
```json
{
  "status": true,
  "message": "...",
  "data": {
    "contents": [],
    "meta": { "page": 1, "limit": 10, "total": 100 }
  }
}
```

**Success (Single):**
```json
{
  "status": true,
  "message": "...",
  "data": {}
}
```

**Error:**
```json
{
  "status": false,
  "message": "...",
  "errors": []
}
```

